track_notes: Start at the Tangle Falls Trailhead.  The first 3 km will be on a trail but the remainder is all off trail, and in an area that receives hardly any visitors.  You will basically follow Tangle Creek until you see the low col on Tangle Ridge.  Go across the col to the Beauty Creek Valley and make your way up the valley.  We choose to access the summit of Andover Peak via a steep scree slope on the Southwest side.
